        <updateDate>2020-06-18T14:51:43Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong></strong><b>National Guard and Reservists Debt Relief Extension Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill extends for an additional four years the exemption from the means test under Chapter 7 bankruptcy for qualifying members of an Armed Forces reserve component or the National Guard. Currently, the exemption expires on December 19, 2019. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
